Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.55,0:00:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.45,0:00:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑛  等等  今天我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.28,0:00:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到更忙的时候再来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然看着夹在婆婆们中间显得格格不入的小一也挺有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真失礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没格格不入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.17,0:00:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可说不准哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  连春日野君都…
